          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SLA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " This experiment determined the total cross",
                "section for the population of this state in the (d,n)",
                "reaction, but the limited experimental sensitivity to",
                "the neutron-angular distribution does not allow for",
                "the disentanglement of the l=0 and l=2 contributions.",
                "The reaction mechanism was investigated using a CRC",
                "calculation using the program FRESCO. Applying the",
                "mirror-nucleus spectroscopic factors directly would",
                "predict a slightly higher cross section than",
                "measured. We therefore scaled the spectroscopic",
                "factors of Hamill et al. down to reproduce the",
                "observed cross section, while retaining the l=0/l=2",
                "ratio. In order to extract the proton-resonance width",
                "from the l=0 spectroscopic factor, the R-matrix",
                "expression was employed GammaP = C**2*Sl=0*GammaS.P.,",
                "where C**2*Sl=0 is a spectroscopic factor and",
                "GammaS.P. is a single particle width."
              ]
            }
          ],
